- add current release to intern/www/index.html.in, Section "Older
  releases", check file size info of distribution

- use.prj: set Project-Keywords to new version

- add Changelog entry, checkin working version

- create a new major version:

	prcs checkin -r1-1-0-release

- build and test release

	ant all

- copy documentation manually to web site

	cp -rp build/doc/* /home/dbs/www/doc/projects/USE-x.y.z

- copy new release to save place, copy all releases to web site

	cp use-*.tar.gz use-*.zip ~/work/java/use-releases
	cp ~/work/java/use-releases/* /home/dbs/www/doc/projects/USE-x.y.z

- check WWW home page and download links

- send mail to use-announce

- approve bounced mail in gnus with `|' and /home/majordomo/bin/approve
